           * HEA Title IV, Parts C, D, E, F, G & H
           * HEA Titles V, VI & VII

  bullet Volume II - Elementary and Secondary Education, Individuals With
         Disabilities, And Related Programs As Amended Through December 31,
         1998, 106th Congress, 1st Session (Serial No. 106-A)
          1. Cover and Table of Contents
          2. Elementary and Secondary Education Act
          3. National Education Statistics Act
          4. Indian Self Determination and Education Assistance Act
          5. Indian Education Assistance Act
          6. Snyder Act and Johnson-OMalley Act
          7. Indian Education: LEA programs and BIA Programs
          8. Tribally Controlled Schools Act
          9. Refugee and Immigrant Education and Stewart B. McKinney Homeless
             Assistance Act
         10. Individuals with Disabilities Education Act
         11. Goals 2000: Educate America Act
         12. Child Nutrition Act
         13. Richard B. Russell National School Lunch Act
         14. Improving Americas Schools Act: Miscellaneous programs
         15. Education for Economic Security Act: NSF, Math, Science and
             Engineering, Asbestos School Hazard Abatement, and the Equal Access
             Act
         16. Grants to Insular Areas
         17. Anti-Drug Abuse Act
         18. Handicapped Childrens Protection Act

